A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F08150257%2Fimage-1699.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%20the%20Indian%20Telegraph%20Act%20of%201885%20was%20conceived%2C%20India%20was%20still%20under%20the%20rule%20of%20the%20British%20Raj.%20The%20telegraph%20had%20become%20an%20important%20tool%20for%20British%20dominion%20over%20India%20by%20quelling%20rebellions%20and%20consolidating%20information.%20It%20was%2C%20therefore%2C%20important%20for%20the%20British%20to%20have%20control%20of%20telegraphy%20and%20infrastructure%20across%20the%20subcontinent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20few%20years%2C%20the%20administration%20has%20handed%20itself%20new%20powers%20that%20tighten%20controls%20over%20online%20content%2C%20allowing%20authorities%20to%20legally%20intercept%20messages%2C%20break%20encryption%2C%20and%20shut%20down%20telecom%20networks%20during%20moments%20of%20political%20turmoil.%20According%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.statista.com%2Fstatistics%2F1095035%2Findia-number-of-internet-shutdowns%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DBetween%2520January%25202012%2520and%2520June%2Cin%2520the%2520world%2520so%2520far.%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EStatista%3C%2Fem%3E%20data%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20between%20January%202012%20and%20June%202022%2C%20there%20were%20639%20government-imposed%20internet%20shutdowns%20across%20India%2C%20resulting%20in%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20internet%20blocks%20in%20the%20world%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fbbc-documentary-on-narendra-modi-tries-too-hard-to-balance-both-sides%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EIndia%3A%20the%20Modi%20Question%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20examining%20the%202002%20sectarian%20riots%2C%20came%20at%20a%20sensitive%20time%20for%20the%20Union%20government.%20The%20government%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fexplainer-the-emergency-rules-invoked-by-the-govt-to-ban-the-bbc-film-on-gujarat-riots%5C%22%3Einvoked%20emergency%20laws%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20ban%20links%20and%20clips%20of%20the%20documentary%20from%20being%20shared%20online%2C%20which%20YouTube%20and%20Twitter%20complied%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20December%2024%2C%202023%2C%20the%20Telecommunications%20Act%2C%202023%20was%20published%20in%20the%20official%20gazette%2C%20after%20the%20Bill%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Fcontroversial-telecom-bill-becomes-act-in-absence-of-suspended-opposition-mps%5C%22%3Ewas%20passed%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20both%20Houses%20of%20the%20Parliament%20and%20received%20the%20Presidential%20assent.%20The%20Act%20promises%20a%20tectonic%20shift%20in%20the%20legal%20framework%20relating%20to%20telecommunications%20in%20India%2C%20by%20demolishing%20the%20more%20than%20a%20century%20old%20Indian%20Telegraph%20Act%2C%201885%20and%20other%20laws%20that%20have%20so%20far%20formed%20the%20basis%20of%20governing%20the%20telecom%20space%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Ftelecom-bill-2023-is-a-repackaged-version-of-the-archaic-colonial-law%5C%22%3ETelecom%20Bill%202023%20Is%20a%20Repackaged%20Version%20of%20the%20Archaic%20Colonial%20Law%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Act%20comes%20at%20a%20juncture%20of%20time%20when%20India%20is%20leapfrogging%20in%20the%205G%20era%20and%20consumption%20of%20telecom%20services%20is%20skyrocketing.%20There%20is%20an%20imminent%20need%20for%20a%20governance%20and%20regulatory%20framework%20that%20is%20in%20sync%20with%20the%20needs%20of%20the%20telecom%20industry%20as%20well%20as%20to%20foster%20development%20of%20new%20technologies.%20The%20licence%20regime%20under%20the%20prevailing%20laws%20is%20sought%20to%20be%20converted%20to%20an%20%E2%80%98authorisation%E2%80%99%20framework.%20Pertinently%2C%20the%20trigger%20points%20for%20obtaining%20authorisations%20have%20been%20enhanced.%20As%20far%20as%20existing%20licences%2C%20registrations%20and%20permissions%20are%20concerned%2C%20they%20will%20have%20to%20be%20eventually%20migrated%20to%20the%20new%20regime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20defining%20telecommunication%20services%20as%20%E2%80%9Cany%20service%20for%20telecommunication%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20government%20may%20have%20just%20opened%20up%20Pandora%E2%80%99s%20box.%20Any%20telecommunication%20service%2C%20which%20could%20arguably%20include%20OTT%20(over%20the%20top)%20and%20M2M%20(machine%20to%20machine)%20services%20as%20well%2C%20can%20potentially%20fall%20within%20this%20ambit%20and%20trigger%20a%20requirement%20to%20obtain%20an%20authorisation.%20Hence%2C%20it%20may%20not%20be%20safe%20to%20assume%20for%20the%20time%20being%20that%20OTT%20services%20are%20beyond%20the%20clutches%20of%20the%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUse%20of%20verifiable%20biometric-based%20identification%20is%20yet%20another%20data%20tinderbox%20awaiting%20rampage%20by%20cyber%20criminals.%20All%20authorised%20entities%20are%20required%20to%20employ%20verifiable%20biometric-based%20identification%20mechanisms%20(as%20may%20be%20prescribed)%20for%20identifying%20persons%20to%20whom%20telecom%20services%20are%20provided.%20This%20is%20not%20only%20likely%20to%20limit%20the%20way%20in%20which%20subscriber%20verification%20formalities%20can%20be%20carried%20out%2C%20but%20also%20raise%20concerns%20relating%20to%20privacy%20and%20cybersecurity%20as%20storage%20of%20biometric%20data%20and%20records%20bring%20along%20its%20set%20of%20challenges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20government%20can%20notify%20standards%20and%20conformity%20assessments%20for%20matters%20relating%20to%20cybersecurity%20for%20telecommunication%20services%20and%20networks%2C%20encryption%2C%20and%20data%20processing%20in%20telecommunication%2C%20etc.%20This%20might%20lead%20to%20an%20overlap%20with%20provisions%20under%20the%20information%20technology%20framework%2C%20which%20applies%20horizontally%20to%20all%20sectors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20recent%20past%2C%20the%20government%20has%20released%20specific%20laws%20and%20regulations%20dealing%20with%20these%20very%20aspects%2C%20such%20as%20the%20directions%20issued%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pib.gov.in%2FPressReleasePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1820904%5C%22%3EIndian%20Computer%20Emergency%20Response%20Team%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fwhat-lies-beneath-the-pr-blitz-on-the-new-data-protection-act%5C%22%3E%20Digital%20Personal%20Data%20Protection%20(DPDP)%20Act%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20etc.%20This%20may%20culminate%20in%20multiplicity%20of%20compliances%20for%20entities%2C%20which%20will%20ultimately%20impact%20the%20ease%20of%20doing%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChapter%20IV%2C%20Article%2020%20of%20the%20new%20Telecommunications%20Act%2C%202023%20has%20some%20alarming%20provisions.%20The%20Bill%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9COn%20the%20occurrence%20of%20any%20public%20emergency%2C%20including%20disaster%20management%2C%20or%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20public%20safety%2C%20the%20Central%20Government%20or%20a%20State%20Government%20or%20any%20officer%20specially%20authorised%20in%20this%20behalf%20by%20the%20Central%20Government%20or%20a%20State%20Government%2C%20if%20satisfied%20that%20it%20is%20necessary%20or%20expedient%20so%20to%20do%2C%20by%20notification%20%E2%80%93%20(a)%20take%20temporary%20possession%20of%20any%20telecommunication%20service%20or%20telecommunication%20network%20from%20an%20authorised%20entity%3B%20or%20(b)%20provide%20for%20appropriate%20mechanism%20to%20ensure%20that%20messages%20of%20a%20user%20or%20group%20of%20users%20authorised%20for%20response%20and%20recovery%20during%20public%20emergency%20are%20routed%20on%20priority.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcleverly-drafted-telecom-bill-government-tightens-grip-digital-india%5C%22%3EWith%20Cleverly%20Drafted%20Telecom%20Bill%2C%20Government%20Tightens%20Grip%20on%20Digital%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAny%20message%20or%20class%20of%20messages%2C%20to%20or%20from%20any%20person%20or%20class%20of%20persons%2C%20to%20or%20from%20any%20(or%20class%20of)%20telecommunication%20equipment%2C%20for%20example%2C%20mobile%20phone%2C%20laptop%2C%20server%2C%20communication%20infrastructure%2C%20etc.%20can%20be%20brought%20under%20the%20custody-authority%20for%20suitable%20actions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPress%20messages%2C%20intended%20to%20be%20published%20in%20India%2C%20and%20of%20correspondents%20accredited%20to%20the%20central%20government%20or%20state%20government%20have%20been%20exempted%20from%20interception%2C%20although%20they%20can%20be%20intercepted%20for%20national%20security%20reasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Article%2022%2C%20the%20Central%20government%20may%20by%20rules%20provide%20for%20the%20measures%20to%20protect%20and%20ensure%20cyber%20security%20of%20telecommunication%20networks%20and%20telecommunication%20services.%20The%20measures%20may%20include%20collection%2C%20analysis%2C%20and%20dissemination%20of%20traffic%20data%20that%20is%20generated%2C%20transmitted%2C%20received%2C%20or%20stored%20in%20telecommunication%20networks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPut%20simply%2C%20for%20the%20purposes%20of%20this%20sub-section%2C%20the%20term%20%E2%80%9Ctraffic%20data%E2%80%9D%20refers%20to%20any%20data%20generated%2C%20transmitted%2C%20received%2C%20or%20stored%20in%20telecommunication%20networks.%20This%20includes%20information%20pertaining%20to%20the%20type%2C%20routing%2C%20duration%2C%20or%20time%20of%20a%20telecommunication.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20challenge%20arises%20in%20how%20respective%20officers%20interpret%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20new%20Act%2C%20which%20empowers%20them%20to%20oversee%20the%20stakeholders%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20telecommunication%20network.%20This%20encompasses%20ordinary%20individuals%2C%20such%20as%20you%20and%20me%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20entities%20involved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EPaul%20Koshy%20is%20a%20consultant%20in%20infrastructure%20development%20and%20engineering.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704709850000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F08150257%2Fimage-1699.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fthe-alarming-provisions-of-indias-new-telecommunications-act%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22By%20defining%20telecommunication%20services%20as%20%E2%80%9Cany%20service%20for%20telecommunication%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20government%20may%20have%20just%20opened%20up%20the%20Pandora%E2%80%99s%20box.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fthe-alarming-provisions-of-indias-new-telecommunications-act%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20survived%20the%20'Miracle%20on%20the%20Hudson'%20flight%20that%20crash-landed%2015%20years%20ago.%20The%20JAL%20accident%20brings%20it%20all%20back.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221026%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Passenger%20Diane%20Higgins%20and%20Captain%20Chelsey%20%26quot%3BSully%26quot%3B%20Sullenberger.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65983b6cec62ab5daf811bbc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22770%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDiane%20Higgins%20and%20Captain%20Chesley%20%26quot%3BSully%26quot%3B%20Sullenberger.%20Higgins%20was%20a%20passenger%20on%20the%20%26quot%3BMiracle%20on%20the%20Hudson%26quot%3B%20flight%2C%20and%20Sullenberger%20was%20the%20pilot%20who%20safely%20landed%20the%20plane.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Diane%20Higgins%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EFifteen%20years%20ago%2C%20a%20fully%20loaded%20airliner%20crash-landed%20in%20the%20Hudson%20River.%20Everyone%20survived.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAnother%20miracle%20just%20happened%20in%20Tokyo%20%E2%80%94%20where%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjapan-airlines-crash-swiss-cheese-holes-may-explain-collision-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E379%20people%20escaped%20a%20burning%20Japan%20Airlines%3C%2Fa%3E%20plane.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BMiracle%20on%20the%20Hudson%26quot%3B%20passenger%20Diane%20Higgins%20says%20the%20JAL%20accident%20triggers%20memories.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Diane%20Higgins%2C%20one%20of%20the%20155%20people%20who%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fphotos-show-a320-jet-that-crash-landed-the-hudson-river-2022-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Esurvived%20the%20%26quot%3BMiracle%20on%20the%20Hudson%26quot%3B%20crash%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20alongside%20her%20mother%2C%20Lucille%20Palmer%2C%20in%202009.%20It%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%2085%20years%20old%2C%20my%20mother%20was%20the%20oldest%20person%20on%20the%20plane%20when%20it%20crash-landed.%20Her%20name%20was%20Lucille%20Palmer%2C%20but%20everyone%20called%20her%20%26quot%3BLulu.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20were%20in%20seats%2017E%20and%2017F%2C%20and%20my%20mom%20had%20to%20be%20helped%20off%20in%20a%20wheelchair.%20The%20experience%20was%20very%20scary%20%E2%80%94%20it%20was%20nothing%20you'd%20ever%20want%20to%20go%20through%20%E2%80%94%20but%20it%20was%20still%20a%20miraculous%20experience.%20All%20155%20passengers%20and%20crew%20survived.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20thankful%20for%20the%20fact%20that%20I'm%20still%20here%20%E2%80%94%20I'm%20so%20blessed%20to%20be%20given%20a%20second%20chance%20at%20life.%20I%20always%20ask%20why%20I%20was%20spared%2C%20and%20people%20tell%20me%20that%20my%20job%20on%20Earth%20wasn't%20done%20yet%2C%20so%20I%20guess%20I%20was%20saved%20for%20a%20reason.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22964%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Miracle%20on%20the%20Hudson%20A320.%5C%22%20charset%3