ary%20to%20look%20at.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221544%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Japan%20Airlines'%20Airbus%20A350%20engulfed%20in%20flames%20on%20the%20runway%20of%20Haneda%20International%20Airport%20in%20Tokyo%2C%20Japan%20on%20January%202%2C%202024.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65983b191c5c7b8c9a0e6552%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221158%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Japan%20Airlines%20Airbus%20A350%20collided%20with%20a%20coast%20guard%20plane%20in%20Tokyo%20on%20Wednesday.%3Cp%3EIssei%20Kato%2FReuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20some%20of%20the%20passengers%20said%20in%20interviews%20that%20it%20was%20something%20of%20a%20miracle%2C%20I%20thought%3A%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%2C%20I%20can%20believe%20that.%20Divine%20intervention%20for%20you%2C%20too.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ELife%20has%20been%20good%20in%20the%2015%20years%20since%20the%20accident%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20a%20second%20chance%20helped%20me%20live%20by%20looking%20at%20the%20positives%20and%20not%20getting%20so%20caught%20up%20in%20everyday%20life.%20In%20the%2015%20years%20since%20the%20accident%2C%20I've%20welcomed%20three%20new%20grandchildren%2C%20with%20another%20on%20the%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20sisters%20and%20I%20were%20able%20to%20nurse%20my%20mother%20when%20she%20was%20in%20decline.%20I%20was%20also%20able%20to%20be%20there%20for%20my%20daughter%20when%20her%20husband%20was%20sick%20with%20cancer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22505%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lucille%20Palmer%2C%20Diane%20Higgins%2C%20and%20Sully%20after%20the%20Miracle%20on%20the%20Hudson%20accident.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65983b326979d7371820d973%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22379%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELucille%20Palmer%20(L)%20died%20in%202015%20at%2091%20years%20ago.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Diane%20Higgins%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%