ef%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fpolitics-and-nation%2Fpm-narendra-modi-lauds-bohra-community-for-peace-and-development%2Farticleshow%2F65816612.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Ethe%20Bohri%20community%20has%20displayed%20admiration%20for%20Modi%3C%2Fa%3E%20since%20his%20days%20as%20chief%20minister%20of%20Gujarat.%20The%20community%20continues%20to%20be%20fervent%20admirers%20and%20are%20regularly%20seen%20in%20his%20diaspora%20events%20internationally.%20The%20government%20also%20showcased%20a%20successful%20Muharram%20procession%20by%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20Shias%20as%20a%20sign%20of%20normalcy%20in%20the%20Valley%20post%20the%20abrogation%20of%20Article%20370.%20Modi%20has%20bifurcated%20the%20Muslim%20community%20into%20these%20favourable%20groupings%20of%20potential%20allies%20rather%20than%20ignoring%20them%20as%20a%20lost%20vote%20bank.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fnot-in-our-name-over-3000-christians-dissociate-from-pm-modis-christmas-lunch%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Not%20in%20Our%20Name%E2%80%99%3A%20Over%203%2C000%20Christians%20Dissociate%20From%20PM%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20Christmas%20Lunch%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20purpose%20does%20this%20serve%20for%20Modi%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20certainly%20does%20not%20need%20the%20additional%20minority%20vote%20bank%2C%20but%20it%20has%20multiple%20benefits.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFirst%2C%20it%20matters%20for%20his%20narrative%20and%20projection%20to%20the%20outside%20world%2C%20despite%20whatever%20his%20rabble-rouser%20election%20spokespeople%20say%20and%20do.%20The%20image%20of%20a%20free%2C%20multi-cultural%2C%20secular%20India%20must%20be%20projected%20in%20the%20international%20world.%20Secondly%2C%20it%20provides%20the%20BJP%20vote%20bank%20with%20a%20few%20cherry-picked%20niceties%20to%20showcase%20that%20Modi%20is%20loved%20by%20all%2C%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20only%20propaganda%20that%20displays%20anything%20to%20the%20contrary.%20Thirdly%2C%20while%20the%20BJP%20may%20or%20may%20not%20get%20a%20sizeable%20winning%20vote%20bank%20from%20this%20outreach%2C%20it%20helps%20it%20prevent%20the%20wholesale%20transfer%20of%20these%20votes%20en%20bloc%20to%20the%20opposition.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20the%20flip%20side%2C%20for%20these%20hand-picked%20minorities%20who%20do%20not%20mind%20playing%20to%20the%20gallery%2C%20it%20is%20a%20chance%20to%20be%20the%20chosen%20few%20who%20are%20favoured%20by%20the%20government.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20the%20opposition%20is%20caught%20between%20being%20soft%20or%20visibly%20Hindu%2C%20it%20has%20chosen%20to%20take%20the%20minorities%20for%20granted.%20Minorities%20have%20languished%20without%20effective%20bargaining%20power%20because%20in%20the%20fight%20for%20survival%2C%20their%20options%20remain%20limited%20to%20the%20%E2%80%98secular%E2%80%99%20opposition.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ETherefore%2C%20the%20true%20loser%20in%20this%20debate%20is%20the%20average%20minority%20citizen.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20changing%20political%20space%2C%20minority%20votes%20are%20not%20openly%20courted%20as%20kingmakers.%20And%20in%20cases%20where%20they%20are%2C%20the%20opposition%20is%20faced%20with%20new%20dilemmas.%20In%20the%20recent%20assembly%20elections%20in%20Telangana%2C%20the%20Congress%20released%20a%20minority%20declaration%20with%20the%20hope%20of%20swinging%20these%20votes%2C%20which%20it%20may%20just%20have.%20However%2C%20it%20faces%20a%20new%20crisis%20as%20it%20has%20no%20Muslim%20MLA.%20All%20its%20Muslim%20candidates%20lost%20the%20election.%20Without%20a%20voice%20from%20the%20government%20in%20the%20legislature%2C%20it%20must%20resort%20to%20nominating%20a%20Muslim%20to%20the%20Telangana%20Legislative%20Council.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnarendra-modi-india-alliance-rahul-gandhi-2024%5C%22%3EThere%E2%80%99s%20Nothing%20%E2%80%98Inevitable%E2%80%99%20About%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20Return%20in%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMinorities%20in%20India%20continue%20to%20lag%20on%20most%20socio-economic%20indicators%20and%20face%20communal%20toxicity%20everyday.%20Yet%2C%20the%20BJP%20touts%20its%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3ESabka%20Saath%20Sabka%20Vikas%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%20model.%20In%20certain%20government%20schemes%2C%20minorities%20like%20Muslims%20and%20Christians%20receive%20a%20slightly%20larger%20proportion%20of%20benefits%20than%20their%20proportion%20of%20the%20population.%20In%202021%2C%20UP%20chief%20minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20claimed%20that%20Muslims%20who%20comprise%2017%25-18%25%20of%20the%20population%20disproportionately%20make-up%2034%25-35%25%20of%20beneficiaries%20of%20BJP%20governments%E2%80%99%20welfare%20schemes%2C%20thus%20demonstrating%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20benevolence.%20However%2C%20this%20actually%20demonstrates%20the%20disproportionate%20weaker%20economic%20status%20of%20Muslims%20owing%20to%20years%20of%20marginalisation%2C%20in%20contrast%20to%20the%20dominant%20myth%20of%20minority%20appeasement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20intent%20becomes%20clearer%20when%20one%20looks%20at%20the%20reduction%20of%20targeted%20and%20specific%20policies.%20In%20the%202023%20budget%2C%20a%20whopping%2038%25%20was%20slashed%20from%20the%20minority%20affairs%20ministry%E2%80%99s%20allocation.%20Yet%2C%20we%20live%20in%20a%20make-believe%20of%20%E2%80%9Cjustice%20for%20all%2C%20appeasement%20of%20none%E2%80%9D.%20Also%2C%20ahead%20of%20the%20elections%2C%20the%20government%20seems%20to%20be%20readying%20to%20frame%20the%20rules%20for%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%2C%20which%20had%20triggered%20nationwide%20protests%20especially%20from%20minorities%20that%20were%20curtailed%20only%20because%20of%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20Modi%20continues%20to%20embrace%20his%20chosen%20minorities%2C%20and%20his%20rabble-rousers%20continue%20to%20intimidate%20and%20spread%20discord%2C%20the%20opposition%20too%20is%20failing%20to%20piece%20together%20a%20coherent%20strategy.%20What%20minorities%20need%20is%20neither%20appeasement%20nor%20benevolence%2C%20but%20rather%20a%20seat%20at%20the%20table%20where%20they%20can%20participate%20in%20decision-making.%20Meaningful%20representation%20involves%20allowing%20minority%20concerns%20to%20be%20raised%20and%20addressed%20effectively.%20Lest%20minorities%20are%20left%20with%20searching%20for%20their%20version%20of%20the%20BJP%20within%20their%20own%20religious%20community.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EAmaan%20Asim%20graduated%20from%20Ashoka%20University%20with%20a%20major%20in%20political%20science%20and%20is%20a%20political%20consultant%20to%20leaders%20across%20multiple%20political%20parties.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704708007000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F30194902%2FEffect-49.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwhat-does-bjps-outreach-to-minority-communities-mean-for-the-opposition%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20BJP%20may%20or%20may%20not%20get%20a%20sizeable%20winning%20vote%20bank%20from%20this%20outreach%2C%20but%20it%20may%20help%20it%20prevent%20the%20wholesale%20transfer%20of%20these%20votes%20en%20bloc%20to%20the%20opposition.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwhat-does-bjps-outreach-to-minority-communities-mean-for-the-opposition%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bet%20your%20career%20on%20these%206%20climate%20jobs%20in%202024%20%E2%