%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20green%20skills%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsustainability-jobs-skills-gap-energy-transition-solar-carbon-emissions-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eare%20in%20high%20demand%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20assembly%20line%20to%20the%20C-suite.%20As%20BI%20previously%20reported%2C%20there%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-you-should-become-electrician-apprenticeship-job-growth-career-trend-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Earen't%20enough%20electricians%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20hook%20up%20homes%20and%20businesses%20with%20greener%20appliances%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fclimate-jobs-pay-startups-big-tech-layoffs-sustainability-engineers-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eclimate%20tech%20companies%3C%2Fa%3E%20need%20engineers%20from%20legacy%20industries%20like%20manufacturing%2C%20oil%20and%20gas%2C%20and%20construction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20C-suite%2C%20financial%20executives%20who%20understand%20ESG%20reporting%20are%20key%2C%20Dawn%20Dzurilla%2C%20founder%20%26amp%3B%20managing%20partner%20of%20Gaia%20Human%20Capital%20Consultants%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJob%20site%20Indeed%20pulled%20data%20on%20the%20fastest-growing%20green%20jobs%20between%20January%201%2C%202023%2C%20and%20January%204%2C%202024.%20Here%20are%20the%20top%20six%20and%20the%20average%20salary%2C%20according%20to%20Indeed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESolar%20Technician%2C%20%2465%2C700%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20number%20of%20solar%20technician%20jobs%20posted%20on%20Indeed%20jumped%20by%2095%25%20over%20the%20past%20year%2C%20making%20it%20the%20fastest-growing%20green%20career%20on%20the%20site.%20Solar%20technicians%20might%20start%20out%20installing%20panels%20and%20troubleshooting%20electrical%20or%20mechanical%20issues.%20As%20they%20advance%2C%20the%20job%20could%20be%20more%20of%20a%20project%20management%20role%2C%20according%20to%20Indeed.%20The%20career%20pathway%20typically%20involves%20a%20several-year%20apprenticeship%20program%20with%20classroom%20and%20on-the-job%20training.%20Some%20states%20require%20solar%20technicians%20to%20be%20licensed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EEnvironmental%20Planner%2C%20%2492%2C470%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EJob%20postings%20for%20environmental%20planners%20grew%20by%2047%25%20over%20the%20last%20year.%20The%20job%20involves%20evaluating%20corporate%20and%20government%20projects%20and%20finding%20ways%20to%20limit%20their%20impact%20on%20water%2C%20land%2C%20and%20biodiversity.%20They%20also%20make%20sure%20these%20projects%20comply%20with%20laws%20and%20regulations%2C%20playing%20a%20key%20role%20in%20obtaining%20environmental%20permits%20for%20construction%2C%20Indeed%20said.%20The%20position%20requires%20degrees%20in%20civil%20or%20environmental%20engineering%20and%20a%20certificate%20from%20the%20American%20Institute%20of%20Certified%20Planners.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EEnergy%20Consultant%2C%20%2493%2C835%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEnergy%20consultant%20is%20a%20relatively%20new%20job%2C%20Indeed%20said%2C%20and%20involves%20advising%20companies%2C%20governments%2C%20and%20other%20institutions%20on%20how%20to%20cut%20back%20their%20overall%20energy%20use.%20This%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20helps%20reduce%20greenhouse%20gas%20emissions.%20Postings%20on%20Indeed%20jumped%20by%20more%20than%2031%25%20in%20the%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20bachelor's%20degree%20in%20physics%2C%20engineering%2C%20or%20renewable%20energy%20management%20is%20a%20good%20start.%20There%20are%20also%20renewable%20energy%20and%20green%20building%20certification%20programs%20for%20people%20with%20high%20school%20or%20college%20degrees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECivil%20Engineer%2C%20%2493%2C960%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECivil%20engineers%20design%20and%20supervise%20big%20infr