on%2C%20Ms%20Maxwell%20declared%20her%20intention%20to%20proceed%20with%20an%20appeal%20for%20the%20dismissal%20of%20case%20filed%20against%20her%20by%C2%A0Virginia%20Giuffre.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20attorneys%20said%20in%20a%20statement%2C%20%E2%80%9CGhislaine%20Maxwell%20took%20no%20position%20on%20the%20Court's%20recent%20decision%20to%20unseal%20documents%20in%20Giuffre%20v.%20Maxwell%20as%20these%20disclosures%20have%20no%20bearing%20on%20her%20or%20her%20pending%20appeal.%20Ghislaine's%20focus%20is%20on%20the%20upcoming%20appellate%20argument%20asking%20for%20her%20entire%20case%20to%20be%20dismissed.%20She%20is%20confident%20that%20she%20will%20obtain%20justice%20in%20the%20Second%20Circuit%20Court%20of%20Appeals.%20She%20has%20consistently%20and%20vehemently%20maintained%20her%20innocence%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20Independent%20reported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ELast%20month%2C%20a%20significant%20ruling%20by%20US%20District%20Judge%20Loretta%20Preska%20allowed%20the%20release%20of%20documents%2C%20including%20the%20unsealing%20of%20names%2C%20after%20January%201.%20While%20the%20judge%20protected%20the%20identities%20of%20some%20Epstein%20victims%2C%20she%20insisted%20that%20the%20names%20of%20Epstein's%20associates%2C%20known%20as%20%26quot%3BJohn%20and%20Jane%20Does%2C%26quot%3B%20should%20be%20disclosed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThis%20decision%20has%20brought%20several%20well-known%20figures%20into%20the%20spotlight%2C%20including%20former%20President%20Bill%20Clinton%2C%20Stephen%20Hawking%2C%20Prince%20Andrew%2C%20and%20Donald%20Trump.%20In%20a%20recently%20unsealed%20deposition%2C%20Johanna%20Sjoberg%20testified%20that%20%E2%80%9C%5BEpstein%5D%20said%20one%20time%20that%20Clinton%20likes%20them%20young%2C%E2%80%9D%20referring%20to%20girls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ENew%20details%20have%20emerged%20from%20Ghislaine%20Maxwell's%20case%20following%20the%20unsealing%20of%20documents%2C%20revealing%20that%20she%20did%20not%20attend%20a%20deposition%20after%20being%20subpoenaed%20in%202009.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20disgraced%20British%20socialite%20was%20summoned%20to%20testify%20in%20a%20case%20initiated%20by%20Virginia%20Giuffre.%20Ms%20Maxwell%2C%20who%20initially%20agreed%20to%20participate%2C%20cited%20family%20affairs%20in%20the%20UK%20as%20the%20reason%20for%20her%20unavailability%2C%20later%20informing%20Ms%20Giuffre's%20team%20that%20she%20had%20to%20leave%20the%20country%20due%20to%20her%20mother's%20illness.%20However%2C%20a%20photo%20released%20in%202010%20showed%20Ms%20Maxwell%20attending%20the%20wedding%20of%20Chelsea%20Clinton%2C%20the%20daughter%20of%20Bill%20Clinton%2C%20around%20that%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704706200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F7o9cl6l_jeffrey-epstein-afp_625x300_05_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhow-ghislaine-maxwell-reacted-to-unsealing-of-jeffrey-epstein-files-4822163%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ghislaine%20Maxwell%20is%20currently%20serving%20a%2020-year%20sentence%20for%20helping%20Jeffrey%20Epstein%20in%20recruiting%20and%20grooming%20underage%20girls.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhow-ghislaine-maxwell-reacted-to-unsealing-of-jeffrey-epstein-files-4822163%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhow-ghislaine-maxwell-reacted-to-unsealing-of-jeffrey-epstein-files-4822163%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhow-ghislaine-maxwell-reacted-to-unsealing-of-jeffrey-epstein-files-4822163%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tata%20Steel%20fixes%20Jan%2019%20as%20record%20date%20to%20allot%20shares%20to%20TCIL%20shareholders%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A170