20capital%20Bengaluru%20is%20country's%20Silicon%20Valley.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20like%20the%20earlier%20Vibrant%20Gujarat%20summits%2C%20hotel%20rooms%20are%20in%20short%20supply%20now%20and%20getting%20pricier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeeppreet%20Bindra%2C%20general%20manager%20at%20a%20hotel%20run%20by%20Marriott%20International%20in%20Ahmedabad%2C%20which%20is%20about%2030%20km%20away%20from%20Gandhinagar%20and%20where%20many%20of%20the%20summit%20visitors%20will%20be%20staying%2C%20said%20his%20daily%20room%20tariffs%20had%20surged%20to%20%24420%20a%20night%2C%20from%20the%20typical%20%24150%20a%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVisitors%20though%20will%20have%20to%20largely%20skip%20alcohol%20as%20the%20state%20is%20one%20of%20few%20that%20restricts%20public%20liquor%20sales%2C%20unless%20special%20government%20permits%20are%20obtained%20-%20something%20that%20has%20often%20irked%20executives%20working%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20the%20event%2C%20Gujarat%20signed%20initial%20investment%20pacts%20worth%20%24120%20billion%20with%20more%20than%20200%20companies%2C%20including%20steelmaker%20ArcelorMittal's%20local%20joint%20venture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20mainly%20focused%20on%20traditional%20industries%20so%20far%2C%20but%20now%20we%20are%20also%20focusing%20on%20upcoming%20sectors%20such%20as%20semiconductors%2C%20electronics%20and%20EVs%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Rahul%20Gupta%20of%20state%20agency%20Gujarat%20Industrial%20Development%20Corporation.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704705120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F0vdjkje8_vibrant-gujarat-global-summit-reuters_625x300_08_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fprime-minister-narendra-modi-to-lure-tech-electric-vehicles-investments-at-gujarat-summit-as-poll-looms-4821710%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20will%20roll%20out%20the%20red%20carpet%20for%20hundreds%20of%20dom