%20shocking%20details%20about%20disgraced%20British%20socialite%20Ghislaine%20Maxwell's%20activities%20on%20Jeffrey%20Epstein's%20private%20island.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20deposition%20alleges%20that%20Ms%20Maxwell%20swam%20naked%20while%20recruits%20were%20made%20to%20massage%20her%20in%20various%20compromising%20situations%2C%20reports%20Daily%20Mail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20recruits%20involved%20in%20these%20activities%20were%20referred%20to%20by%20Ms%20Maxwell%20as%20her%20%E2%80%9Cchildren.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJohanna%20Sjoberg%2C%20a%2020-year-old%20student%20recruited%20by%20Ms%20Maxwell%2C%20revealed%20that%20she%20was%20compensated%20%C2%A3200%20for%20each%20massage%20session%20with%20the%20pair.%20She%20also%20disclosed%20that%20the%20payment%20increased%20by%20%C2%A3100%20when%20she%20engaged%20in%20explicit%20activities%20with%20Epstein.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%202016%20deposition%2C%20Ms%20Sjoberg%20mentioned%20giving%20around%20five%20to%20ten%20massages%20to%20Ms%20Maxwell%2C%20during%20which%20Ms%20Maxwell%20was%20naked%20under%20a%20towel.%20In%20one%20instance%2C%20Ms%20Sjoberg%20recalled%20Epstein%20entering%20the%20room%20during%20a%20massage%20and%20touching%20Ms%20Maxwell%20inappropriately.%20She%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20do%20recall%20an%20instance%20where%20I%20was%20massaging%20her%20and%20Jeffrey%20%5BEpstein%5D%20came%20into%20the%20room%20and%20he%20did%20something%20sort%20of%20sexual%20to%20her%2C%20whether%20it%20was%20fondling%20her%20or%20slapping%20her%20butt%20or%20something%2C%20and%20she%20brushed%20him%20off%20like%20she%20was%20embarrassed.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20if%20Ms%20Maxwell%20was%20ever%20naked%20or%20topless%20by%20the%20pool%2C%20Ms%20Sjoberg%20couldn't%20recall%20but%20mentioned%20her%20being%20naked%20when%20swimming%20in%20the%20ocean.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20massages%20she%20gave%20Epstein%2C%20she%20said%20she%20was%20naked%20%E2%80%9C25%20to%2050%20percent%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20time.%20However%2C%20Ms%20Sjoberg%20clarified%20that%20Ms%20Maxwell%20never%20acted%20sexually%20towards%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJohanna%20Sjoberg%20revealed%20that%20she%20had%20agreed%20to%20bring%20at%20least%20three%20girls%20to%20Epstein's%20island%2C%20and%20Ms%20Maxwell%20financially%20rewarded%20her%20for%20them.%20Ms%20Sjoberg%20explained%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20did%20bring%20one%20girl...%20that%20I%20had%20worked%20with%20at%20a%20restaurant.%20And%20I%20recall%20Ghislaine%20giving%20me%20money%20to%20bring%20her%20over%3B%20however%2C%20they%20never%20called%20her%20to%20come.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProviding%20graphic%20details%20about%20another%20girl's%20interaction%20with%20Epstein%2C%20she%20recounted%2C%20%E2%80%9CAt%20one%20point%20he%20lifted%20up%20her%20shirt%20and%20exposed%20her%20bra%2C%20and%20she%20grabbed%20it%20and%20pulled%20it%20down.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20unsettling%20details%2C%20Ms%20Sjoberg%20provided%20additional%20insight%20into%20the%20dynamics%20between%20Ghislaine%20Maxwell%20and%20the%20girls%20on%20the%20island.%20According%20to%20Ms%20Sjoberg%2C%20Ghislaine%20Maxwell%20would%20kiss%20all%20the%20girls%20before%20bed%20and%20refer%20to%20them%20as%20her%20%E2%80%9Cchildren.%E2%80%9D%20Furthermore%2C%20Ms%20Sjoberg%20alleged%20that%20Ms%20Maxwell%20frequently%20suggested%20that%20having%20other%20girls%20present%20relieved%20her%20from%20sexual%20pressures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20previously%20released%20documents%2C%20Ms%20Sjoberg%20testified%20that%20she%20started%20working%20for%20Epstein%20in%202001%20at%20the%20age%20of%2020%2C%20having%20been%20recruited%20by%20Ms%20Maxwell%20as%20a%20personal%20assistant.%20She%20claimed%20that%20she%20was%20made%20to%20perform%20sexual%20acts%20immediately.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGhislaine%20Maxwell%20was%20found%20guilty%20in%20December%202021%20and%20is%20now%20facing%20a%2020-year%20prison%20sentence.%20She%20was%20convicted%20of%20helpin