20to%2011%20men%20who%20raped%20Bilkis%20Bano%20and%20killed%20her%20child%20and%20other%20family%20members%20in%202002.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20convicts%20walked%20free%20on%20Independence%20Day%20in%202022%20under%20an%20outdated%20remission%20policy%20of%20the%20Gujarat%20government%2C%20setting%20off%20a%20huge%20political%20controversy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Bano%20approached%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20November%202022%20challenging%20what%20she%20called%20%26quot%3Bpremature%26quot%3B%20release%20of%20the%2011%20convicts%20by%20the%20state%20government.%20She%20said%20the%20remission%20of%20sentence%20has%20%26quot%3Bshaken%20the%20conscience%20of%20society%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELaunching%20a%20scathing%20attack%20on%20the%C2%A0BJP%2C%20Congress%20spokesperson%20Manish%20Doshi%20said%20that%20the%20Gujarat%20government%20%26quot%3Bappears%20to%20work%20to%20save%20the%20culprits%2C%20instead%20of%20getting%20justice%20for%20victims.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20very%20unfortunate%20for%20the%20society%2C%20and%20people%20should%20ensure%20that%20the%20government%20runs%20as%20per%20the%20law.%20The%20government%20has%20failed%20to%20ensure%20justice%20for%20the%20victim%20of%20such%20a%20heinous%20crime%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Doshi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVeteran%20Left%20leader%20Brinda%20Karat%20said%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20order%20%26quot%3Bholds%20some%20hope%20for%20justice%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20comments%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20also%20point%20to%20the%20capability%20of%20the%20Central%20government%20and%20the%20Gujarat%20government%20led%20by%20the%20BJP.%20It%20was%20the%20Gujarat%20government%20that%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20accepted%20the%20documents%2C%20which%20the%20court%20has%20considered%20as%20fraud%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBilkis%20Bano%20was%2021%20years%20old%20-%20five%20months%20pregnant%20-%20when%20she%20was%20raped%20