nd%20abuse%20of%20power%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDwelling%20on%20the%20question%20of%20whether%20the%20convicts%20must%20go%20back%20to%20jail%20in%20the%20context%20of%20their%20right%20to%20personal%20liberty%2C%20the%20top%20court%20decided%20that%20allowing%20them%20to%20remain%20out%20of%20prison%20would%20amount%20to%20validating%20%26quot%3Binvalid%20orders%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20rule%20of%20law%20must%20be%20preserved%20unmindful%20of%20the%20ripples%20of%20the%20consequences%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20judges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20came%20down%20heavily%20on%20its%20own%20judgment%20of%20May%202022%2C%20delivered%20by%20Justice%20Ajay%20Rastogi%20(retired)%2C%20which%20allowed%20the%20convicts%20to%20appeal%20to%20the%20Gujarat%20government%20for%20their%20early%20remission.%20The%20convicts%20got%20the%20order%20%26quot%3Bthrough%20fraudulent%20means%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20judges%20said.%20They%20also%20noted%20that%20the%20Gujarat%20government%20should%20have%20sought%20a%20review%20of%20the%202022%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20convicts%20were%20released%20by%20the%20Gujarat%20government%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20an%20obsolete%201992%20remission%20policy%2C%20which%20has%20since%20been%20superseded%20by%20a%20law%20in%202014%20that%20bars%20the%20release%20of%20convicts%20in%20cases%20of%20capital%20offence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20asked%20Gujarat%20to%20take%20a%20call%20on%20the%20remission%20petition%20of%20one%20of%20the%20convicts%2C%20Radheshyam%20Shah%2C%20the%20state%20government%20consulted%20a%20panel%20that%20included%20men%20linked%20to%20the%20state's%20ruling%20BJP.%20The%20panel%20justified%20approving%20the%20release%20of%20the%20convicts%20saying%20they%20were%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3Esanskari%20%3C%2Fem%3E(cultured)%20Brahmins%26quot%3B%20who%20had%20already%20served%2014%20years%20in%20prison%20and%20had%20displayed%20good%20behaviour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20convicts%20were%20given%20a%20hero's%20welcome%2C%20with%20garlands%20and%20sweets%2C%20and%20they%20were%20seen%20sharing%20stage%20with%20a%20BJP%20MP%20and%20an%20MLA.%20Convict%20Radheshyam%20Shah%20had%20even%20started%20practising%20law%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20was%20told%20during%20an%2011-day%20hearing%20last%20year%20of%20petitions%20challenging%20the%20release%2C%20including%20one%20by%20Bilkis%20Bano.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPetitioners%20against%20the%20convicts'%20release%20included%20Trinamool%20Congress'%20Mahua%20Moitra%2C%20CPM%20Politburo%20member%20Subhashini%20Ali%2C%20independent%20journalist%20Revati%20Laul%20and%20former%20vice-chancellor%20of%20Lucknow%20University%20Roop%20Rekha%20Verma%2C%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20asked%20tough%20questions%20and%20had%20commented%20that%20the%20Gujarat%20government%20was%20on%20%26quot%3Bthin%20ice%26quot%3B%20over%20its%20decision.%20Justices%20BV%20Nagarathna%20and%20Ujjal%20Bhuyan%20had%20asked%20the%20Centre%20and%20the%20Gujarat%20government%20to%20submit%20the%20original%20records%20related%20to%20the%20remission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBilkis%20Bano%20was%2021%20and%20five%20months'%20pregnant%20when%20she%20was%20gang-raped%20while%20fleeing%20during%20the%20communal%20riots%20that%20broke%20out%20after%20the%20fire%20in%20Sabarmati%20Express%20in%20which%2059%20kar%20sevaks%20were%20killed.%20Her%20three-year-old%20daughter%20was%20among%20the%20seven%20family%20members%20slaughtered%20in%20the%20riots.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704699180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-10%2Fk38grgk_bilkis-bano-convicts_625x300_22_October_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbilkis-banos-petition-challenging-early-release-of-her-rapists-in-2002-gujarat-riots-case-valid-says-supreme-court-4820993%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20breakthrough%20in%20Bilkis%20Bano's%20long%20battle%20