0money%20would%20roll%20down%20to%20ticket%20holders%20with%20fewer%20winning%20numbers.%20He%20was%20sure%20that%20the%20mathematical%20flaw%20would%20mean%20guaranteed%20winnings%20if%20he%20bought%20enough%20tickets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr.%20Selbee%2C%20who%20majored%20in%20math%20in%20college%2C%20calculated%20that%20if%20he%20spent%20%241%2C100%20on%201%2C100%20tickets%2C%20odds%20are%20he'd%20have%20one%20four-number%20winner%20that%20would%20pay%20out%20%241%2C000%2C%20and%20at%20least%2018%20or%2019%20three-number%20winners%20that%20paid%20%24900.%20That%20meant%20his%20%241%2C100%20investment%20would%20yield%20a%20%241%2C900%20return%2C%20for%20a%20tidy%20profit%20of%20%24800.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''I%20looked%20at%20the%20odds%2C%20I%20looked%20at%20what%20the%20payoff%20would%20be%20and%20I%20did%20a%20risk-reward%20analysis.%20It%20took%20me%20less%20than%20two%20minutes%20to%20figure%20out%20that%20that%20game%20could%20be%20profitable%2C''%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20initially%20experimented%20by%20investing%20%243%2C600%20in%20Winfall%20tickets%2C%20earning%20approximately%20%246%2C300%20in%20winnings.%20After%20that%2C%20he%20bet%20%248%2C000%20and%20again%20doubled%20his%20money%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20told%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbsnews.com%2Fnews%2Fjerry-and-marge-selbee-how-a-retired-couple-won-millions-using-a-lottery-loophole-60-minutes-2019-06-09%2F%5C%22%3E%20CBS%20News%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20''If%20I%20played%20%241100%2C%20mathematically%20I'd%20have%20one%20four-number%20winner%20%E2%80%93%20that's%201000%20bucks.%20I%20divided%201100%20by%20six%20instead%20of%2057%2C%20because%20I%20did%20a%20mental%20quick%20dirty%2C%20and%20I%20came%20up%20with%2018.%20So%20I%20knew%20I'd%20have%20either%2018%20or%2019%20three-number%20winners%2C%20and%20that's%2050%20bucks%20each.%20At%2018%2C%20I%20got%20%241000%20for%20a%20four-number%20winner%2C%20and%20I%20got%2018%20three-number%20winners%20worth%20%2450%20each%2C%20so%20that's%20900%20bucks.%20So%20I%20got%20%241100%20invested%20and%20I've%20got%20a%20%241900%20return.%20It's%20just%20basic%20arithmetic.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20they%20got%20so%20good%20at%20the%20game%20that%20they%20set%20up%20a%20corporation%2C%20G.S.%20Investment%20Strategies%2C%20and%20invited%20their%20friends%20and%20family%20to%20buy%20into%20the%20business%20for%20%24500%20apiece.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20they%20came%20to%20know%20about%20a%20similar%20Winfall%20lottery%20in%20Massachusetts%2C%20nearly%20700%20miles%20away.%20So%20the%20Selbees%20traveled%20to%20Massachusetts%20every%20time%20there%20was%20a%20rolldown%2C%C2%A0buying%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20tickets%20at%20two%20convenience%20stores.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Selbees%20said%20that%20over%20the%20nine%20years%20they%20played%20Winfall%2C%20their%20group%20won%20a%20total%20of%20%2426%20million%20and%20they%20made%20about%20%248%20million%20in%20profit%20before%20taxes.%C2%A0The%20money%20was%20used%20to%20renovate%20their%20house%20and%20help%20pay%20for%20the%20schooling%20of%20their%20six%20children%2C%2014%20grandchildren%2C%20and%2010%20great-grandchildren.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20winnings%20and%20large%20purchase%20of%20tickets%20also%20triggered%20an%20investigation%20by%20the%20Inspector%20General.%20However%2C%20it%20was%20discovered%20that%20the%20Selbees%20had%20been%20playing%20by%20the%20rules%20and%20there%20was%20nothing%20illegal%20about%20their%20methods.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Selbees'%20story%20now%20has%20become%20the%20inspiration%20for%20the%20new%20movie%20''Jerry%20%26amp%3B%20Marge%20Go%20Large.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704698160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-04%2Fla8o2f1_lottery-650_625x300_25_April_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F