r%20Constitution%3A%20%E2%80%9Cplaces%20like%20Puri%20and%20Dwarka%20would%20still%20have%20held%20on%20in%20toto%20to%20their%20anti-democratic%20and%20anti-egalitarian%20views%20had%20it%20not%20been%20for%20the%20Phules%2C%20Gandhi%2C%20Ambedkar%2C%20and%20the%20like%2C%20challenging%20caste%20discrimination%20on%20the%20ground%20%E2%80%94%20and%20had%20it%20not%20been%20for%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly%20of%20India%2C%20under%20Ambedkar%E2%80%99s%20direction%2C%20rejecting%20the%20Manu%20Smriti%20in%20favour%20of%20a%20democratic%20and%20egalitarian%20Constitution.%20Therefore%2C%20for%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20to%20claim%20a%20congruence%20between%20the%20flag%20%E2%80%98that%20has%20traditionally%20flown%20above%20Hindu%20temples%E2%80%99%20and%20the%20modern%20text%20that%20is%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%20is%20tendentious%20and%20misleading%20(to%20say%20the%20least).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20recent%20analysis%2C%20senior%20advocate%20Indira%20Jaising%20had%20pointed%20out%20how%20%E2%80%98custom%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98culture%E2%80%99%20impacted%20the%20judiciary%20in%202023%2C%20as%20one%20saw%20an%20increasing%20trend%20to%20use%20those%20to%20justify%20imposing%20restrictions%20on%20fundamental%20rights%20or%20writing%20them%20out%20of%20existence.%20She%20writes%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20new%20set%20of%20practices%20has%20replaced%20constitutionalism%20and%20legality%20and%20has%20been%20elevated%20to%20the%20level%20above%20the%20Constitution%20with%20reference%20to%20which%20the%20Constitution%20and%20its%20basic%20features%20are%20to%20be%20interpreted.%20Rights%2C%20as%20we%20know%20them%2C%20are%20replaced%20by%20duties%2C%20negating%20the%20entire%20chapter%20on%20fundamental%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOur%20fundamental%20duties%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22external%20noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fconstitution-day-fundamental-duties-should-be-the-first-priority-of-citizens-says-pm-modi%2Farticleshow%2F95782187.cms%5C%22%20data-wpel-link%3D%5C%22external%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%C2%A0now%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0take%20precedence%20over%20our%20fundamental%20rights.%20We%20must%20all%20do%20our%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22external%20noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fgovernor-tathagata-roy-most-controversial-statements-5594182%5C%22%20data-wpel-link%3D%5C%22external%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ekartavya%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%20without%20any%20expectation%20of%20freedom.%20A%20new%20language%20of%20politics%20and%20consequentially%20law%20has%20been%20invented%20in%20place%20of%20constitutionalism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20are%20told%20that%20there%20is%20an%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20data-wpel-link%3D%5C%22internal%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheleaflet.in%2Fhindu-dharma-has-taken-over-constitutional-values-says-indira-jaising-at-the-sixth-neelabh-mishra-lecture%2F%5C%22%3Eintrinsic%20dharma%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20people%20of%20India%20which%20is%20ancient%20and%20predates%20the%20Constitution.%20Once%20a%20norm%20above%20the%20Constitution%20is%20created%2C%20it%20is%20easy%20to%20see%20why%20there%20is%20no%20need%20to%20amend%20the%20Constitution.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20University%20professor%20Apoorvanand%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fchandrachud-orator-courtroom-judgments-babri-ayodhya%5C%22%3Ealso%20opined%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20how%20CJI%20Chandrachud%20appears%20to%20be%20moving%20away%20from%20his%20job%20of%20dispensing%20justice%2C%20and%20instead%20focusing%20on%20the%20speeches%20he%20makes%20and%20messages%20he%20spreads%20outside%20of%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704692274000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F08110652%2FGDI_UsnWYAA-QMc.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fcji-invokes-