n%20has%20decided%20to%20lease%20out%20electricity%20from%20a%20major%20under-construction%20power%20project%20to%20Rajasthan%20%E2%80%93%20even%20though%20J%26amp%3BK%20has%20been%20facing%20a%20very%20acute%20power%20shortage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ratle%20Hydro%20Electric%20Power%20Corporation%20Limited%20(RHPCL)%2C%20a%20joint%20venture%20between%20NHPC%20Limited%20and%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20State%20Power%20Development%20Corporation%2C%20entered%20into%20a%20power%20purchase%20agreement%20with%20the%20Rajasthan%20Urja%20Vikas%20and%20IT%20Services%20Limited%20for%20offtake%20of%20electricity%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Findia%2Fstarved-of-power-jammu-and-kashmir-sells-power-40-year-rajasthan-deal-sparks-resource-rob-cry%2Fcid%2F1992085%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%20This%20agreement%20was%20reportedly%20signed%20on%20January%203%20in%20Jaipur.%20It%20will%20be%20in%20place%20for%2040%20years%20from%20the%20date%20the%20project%20begins%20commercial%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20winter%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2F16-hour-long-power-cuts-kashmir-faces-unprecedented-crisis%5C%22%3Eit%20was%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20electricity%20production%20in%20Kashmir%20has%20hit%20a%20record%20low%20of%2050-100%20MegaWatts%20(MWs)%20against%20the%20demand%20of%201800%20MWs.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20the%20valley%2C%20home%20to%20over%2070%20lakh%20people%2C%20is%20facing%2012-16%20hour%20long%20power%20cuts%20%E2%80%93%20the%20longest%20in%20the%20last%20two%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20this%20reality%2C%20the%20contract%20to%20lease%20power%20to%20Rajasthan%20has%20created%20outrage%20in%20J%26amp%3BK.%20%E2%80%9CAt%20a%20time%20when%20J%26amp%3BK%20is%20facing%20a%20severe%20power%20crisis%20never%20witnessed%20before%2C%20our%20hydro-electric%20resources%20are%20being%20outsourced%20to%20other%20states.%20Yet%20another%20decision%20th