ow%20to%20make%20payments%20using%20UPI%20Lite%20without%20entering%20a%20PIN.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TIMESOFINDIA.COM%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Truckers'%20Strike%20Exposed%20How%20Hollow%20a%20Law%20Passed%20Without%20Consultation%20Is%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F24153155%2FF6ZBJaLbwAANsqu-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20provision%20of%20harsh%20penalty%20prescribed%20in%20Section%20106%20(2)%20of%20the%20recently%20enacted%20Bharatiya%20Nyaya%20Sanhita%20(BNS)%20for%20offences%20committed%20in%20hit-and-run%20cases%20was%20resented%20by%20truck%20drivers%20who%20described%20it%20as%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Ekaala%20kanoon%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20or%20black%20law.%20They%20went%20on%20strike%20across%20the%20nation%20and%20demanded%20its%20scrapping.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BNS%20was%20brought%20in%20by%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20regime%20in%20place%20of%20the%20colonial-era%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20(IPC).%20It%20was%20passed%20in%20the%20recently%20concluded%20winter%20session%20of%20Parliament%20with%20hardly%20any%20discussion%2C%20and%20that%20too%20after%20144%20Members%20of%20Parliament%20belonging%20to%20several%20opposition%20parties%20were%20suspended%20following%20their%20protest%20when%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20did%20not%20make%20a%20statement%20in%20the%20Parliament%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20breach%20of%20security%20committed%20by%20some%20youth%20who%20trespassed%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20chamber%20and%20released%20gas%20from%20a%20canister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BNS%20provided%20a%20legal%20structure%20to%20make%20drivers%20culpable%20in%20cases%20of%20death%2C%20not%20amounting%20homicide%2C%20caused%20by%20rash%20and%20negligent%20driving%20and%20prescribed%2010%20years%20of%20imprisonment%20or%20a%20fine%20of%20Rs%207%20lakh%20for%20those%20offenders%20who%20flee%20the%20accident%20site%20without%20reporting%20the%20incident%20to%20designated%20authorities.%20This%20new%20penalty%20is%20far%20higher%20than%20the%20two-year%20imprisonment%20prescribed%20in%20the%20IPC%20and%2C%20therefore%2C%20was%20resented%20by%20truck%20drivers%20who%20protested%20against%20the%20stringent%20penal%20provision%20across%20the%20nation%20and%20paralysed%20the%20supply%20chain%20when%20the%20trucks%20and%20lorries%20they%20were%20driving%20came%20to%20stand%20still%20following%20their%20countrywide%20strike.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHome%20ministry%E2%80%99s%20statement%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReckoning%20that%20the%20strike%20has%20caused%20a%20grave%20crisis%20by%20seriously%20disrupting%20the%20supply%20of%20essential%20items%20across%20the%20country%2C%20the%20Union%20home%20secretary%20had%20parleys%20with%20the%20striking%20drivers%20and%20their%20representatives%20on%20January%202%20and%20issued%20a%20statement.%20While%20taking%20cognisance%20of%20the%20concerns%20of%20truckers%20regarding%20the%20provision%20of%2010%20years%20imprisonment%20and%20fine%2C%20under%20Section%20106%20(2)%20of%20BNS%2C%20it%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20these%20new%20laws%20and%20provisions%20have%20not%20yet%20come%20into%20force%20and%20the%20decision%20to%20invoke%20that%20section%20will%20be%20taken%20only%20after%20consultation%20with%20the%20All%20India%20Motor%20Transport%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESadly%2C%20this%20unambiguously%20brings%20out%20the%20crucial%20point%20that%20the%20lawmaking%20process%20anchored%20in%20deliberative%20and%20consultative%20method%20had%20not%20been%20followed%20by%20the%20Modi%20regime%20before%20it%20was%20taken%20up%20in%20the%20Parliament.%20Had%20the%20deliberative%20and%20consultative%20process%20been%20followed%20by%20the%20powers%20that%20be%2C%20the%20Union%20home%20ministry%20would%20have%20engaged%20itself%20with%20the%20association%20of%20drivers%20or%20their%20representatives%20to%20ascertain%20their%20views%20on%20those%20stringent%20measures%20to%20deal%20with%20rash%20and%20negligent%20driving.%20Tragically%2C%20the%20consultation%20is%20now%20going%20to%20take%20place%20after%20the%20law%20has%20been%20enacted%20following%20the%20assent%20it%20has%20got%20from%20the%20President%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Second%20Avatar%20of%20the%20Criminal%20Law%20Bills%3A%20The%20Key%20Changes%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fsecond-avatar-criminal-law-bills-has-anything-changed%5C%22%3ESecond%20Avatar%20of%20the%20Criminal%20Law%20Bills%3A%20The%20Key%20Changes%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMinimum%20government%20and%20maximum%20governance%20exposed%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Modi%20regime%2C%20which%20often%20claimed%20that%20it%20would%20ushering%20in%20the%20era%20of%20%E2%80%98minimum%20government%20and%20maximum%20governance%E2%80%99%2C%20has%20dispensed%20with%20the%20process%20of%20deliberation%20and%20consultation%20for%20framing%20laws%20which%20remain%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20governance.%20It%20is%20quite%20sad%20that%20legislations%20are%20taken%20up%20in%20Parliament%20without%20referring%20most%20of%20these%20to%20the%20department-related%20Parliamentary%20Standing%20Committees%20for%20scrutiny%20and%20examination%20on%20a%20bipartisan%20basis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bills%20are%20now%20passed%20without%20adequate%20discussion%20on%20the%20floor%20of%20both%20the%20Houses%20of%20Parliament%20and%20thereby%20not%20generating%20the%20legislative%20intent%20behind%20those%20Bills%20which%20get%20enacted%20eventually%20by%20employing%20majority%20strength%20of%20the%20ruling%20party.%20It%20is%20well%20known%20that%20Bills%20are%20framed%20by%20government%20departments%20and%2C%20therefore%2C%20these%20represent%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20intent.%20When%20those%20Bills%20are%20adequately%20discussed%20in%20both%20the%20Houses%20of%20the%20Parliament%20and%20its%20clauses%20are%20scrutinised%20and%20debated%2C%20the%20legislative%20intent%20of%20the%20apex%20legislature%20is%20expressed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20rather%20unfortunate%20that%20when%20the%20BNS%20was%20taken%20up%20for%20discussion%2C%20hardly%20two%20hours%20were%20allotted%20for%20discussion%20on%20a%20measure%20which%20aimed%20at%20fundamentally%20altering%20the%20criminal%20code.%20By%20doing%20away%20with%20the%20deliberative%20and%20consultative%20process%20of%20law%20making%2C%20the%20views%20and%20interests%20of%20stakeholders%20are%20lost%20sight%20of%20and%20it%20results%20in%20the%20imposition%20of%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20intent%20on%20the%20citizenry%2C%20who%20are%20hardly%20persuaded%20to%20follow%20that%20law%20in%20the%20making%20of%20which%20they%20had%20no%20role.%20Exactly%20the%20same%20thing%20happened%20to%20four%20farm%20laws%2C%20which%20were%20enacted%20by%20the%20Modi%20regime%20in%202020%20without%20consulting%20the%20farmers%20and%20their%20unions%2C%20and%20only%20after%20the%20massive%20year%20long%20movement%20of%20farmers%20against%20those%20laws%20did%20the%20government%20eventually%20concede%20to%20the%20demand%20of%20farmers%20for%20their%20repeal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20repeal%20of%20the%20farm%20laws%20and%20now%20the%20announcement%20of%20the%20Union%20home%20ministry%20that%20the%20section%20of%20BNS%20dealing%20with%20stringent%20punishment%20for%20drivers%20would%20not%20be%20implemented%20without%20consulting%20them%20clearly%20shows%20that%20the%20law%20making%20process%20followed%20by%20Modi%20regime%20is%20seriously%20flawed%2C%20as%20it%20is%20based%20on%20the%20crude%20majority%20it%20has%20in%20Parliament%20and%20not%20founded%20on%20a%20deliberative%20and%20consultative%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGandhi%E2%80%99s%20warning%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20January%2016%2C%201948%2C%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20had%20thoughtfully%20sai