helping%20others.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETaking%20Jute%20To%20the%20Global%20Stage%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202015%2C%20after%20several%20years%20of%20working%20with%20various%20NGOs%2C%20Chaitali%20laid%20the%20foundation%20for%20the%20Rakshak%20Foundation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20foundation%20focuses%20on%20empowering%20male%20and%20female%20inmates%20and%20other%20underprivileged%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20began%20my%20work%20at%20the%20correctional%20home%2C%20initially%20focusing%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F247834%2Ftechnology-teacher-training-madhya-pradesh-government-schools-english-classes%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espoken%20English%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Over%20time%2C%20I%E2%80%99ve%20undertaken%20various%20projects%2C%20including%20activities%20such%20as%20cookie-making%20with%20women%20and%20inmates%2C%20introducing%20yoga%20(especially%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic)%2C%20engaging%20in%20woodwork%2C%20and%20conducting%20painting%20sessions.%20The%20array%20of%20projects%20reflects%20the%20diverse%20initiatives%20I%E2%80%99ve%20been%20involved%20in%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20project%20that%20has%20gained%20significant%20traction%20is%20%E2%80%9CJute%20Story%20Beyond%20Bars%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fjute-root-4-1704377114.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22She%20has%20also%20trained%203000%20inmates%20with%20the%20help%20of%20the%20government.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fjute-root-4-1704377114.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fjute-root-4-1704377114-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fjute-root-4-1704377114-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fjute-root-4-1704377114-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fjute-root-4-1704377114-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-337531%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EShe%20has%20also%20trained%203000%20inmates%20with%20the%20help%20of%20the%20government.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Chaitali%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20India%2C%20especially%20in%20Bengal%2C%20the%20jute%20industry%20involves%20approximately%2040%20lakh%20people.%20We%20have%20actively%20engaged%20inmates%20in%20crafting%20jute%20products%2C%20showcasing%20their%20creations%20at%20various%20locations%2C%20including%20different%20chambers%20and%20events%20on%20both%20national%20and%20international%20platforms%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20train%20and%20incubate%20these%20inmates%2C%20she%20connected%20with%20the%20National%20Jute%20Board%20of%20India%20(NJB).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20training%20program%20spans%2045%20days%2C%20and%20we%20are%20proud%20to%20have%20partnered%20with%20NJB%20for%20its%20successful%20implementation.%20Our%20initial%20accomplishment%20was%20the%20training%20conducted%20at%20the%20Dandam%20Central%20Correctional%20Home%2C%20benefiting%20the%20prisoners%20there.%20Subsequently%2C%20I%20extended%20the%20initiative%20by%20providing%20additional%20training%2C%20leading%20to%20continued%20production%20and%20participation%20in%20various%20exhibitions%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20promote%20acceptance%20and%20usage%2C%20the%20organisation%20implemented%20a%20practice%20of%20free%20gifting%20initially.%20This%20strategy%20aims%20to%20introduce%20people%20to%20th