4%2F01%2Fjute-root-1-1704376993-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fjute-root-1-1704376993-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fjute-root-1-1704376993-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fjute-root-1-1704376993-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-337527%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20startup%20produces%20jute%20products%20such%20as%20handicrafts%2C%20rugs%2C%20and%20handbags.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Chaitali%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20offer%20a%20diverse%20range%20of%20products%20specifically%20designed%20for%20young%20individuals.%20One%20effective%20way%20we%20showcase%20these%20products%20is%20through%20fashion-oriented%20presentations.%20For%20instance%2C%20we%20feature%20scenarios%20where%20students%2C%20fresh%20out%20of%20university%20or%20college%2C%20are%20seen%20carrying%20jute%20bags.%20This%20not%20only%20generates%20interest%20but%20also%20serves%20as%20a%20visual%20platform%20to%20display%20the%20products%20tailored%20for%20this%20age%20group%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20while%20her%20productions%20are%20going%20up%2C%20she%20still%20hopes%20that%20more%20people%20use%20jute.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20back%20at%20her%20journey%20and%20pondering%20on%20why%20she%20chose%20inmates%20for%20this%20particular%20program%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20often%20view%20those%20involved%20in%20the%20correctional%20system%20as%20wrongdoers%20or%20offenders%2C%20carrying%20a%20mindset%20that%20they%20deserve%20punishment.%20However%2C%20when%20these%20individuals%20engage%20in%20crafting%20products%2C%20especially%20for%20the%20betterment%20of%20the%20environment%2C%20a%20shift%20in%20perception%20occurs.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%20begin%20