%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Alpha%20Monitor%20has%20two%20parts%2C%20one%2C%20a%20wearable%20watch-like%20device%2C%20and%20the%20second%2C%20an%20alarm%20which%20connects%20to%20it.%C2%A0%20The%20wearable%20device%20is%20completely%20customisable%20according%20to%20the%20requirements%20of%20the%20patient.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20strap%20on%20the%20device%20on%20the%20patient.%20In%20case%20the%20patient%20throws%20it%20away%20or%20doesnt%20like%20wearing%20it%2C%20you%20can%20just%20put%20it%20in%20a%20bag%20and%20fix%20it%20in%20their%20pocket%20or%20sock%20or%20wherever%20you%20like.%20Once%20you%20plug%20in%20the%20alarm%2C%20you%20will%20be%20alerted%20for%20every%20tiny%20change%20in%20movement.%20As%20soon%20as%20the%20patient%20gets%20up%20or%20wanders%20away%2C%20it%20will%20alert%20the%20family%20members%20with%20a%20huge%20alarm%20sound%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Hemesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20wearable%20device%20monitors%20body%20temperature%2C%20pulse%2C%20detects%20posture%20and%20movement%2C%20falls%20and%20more.%20It%20works%20using%20a%20gyroscope%20sensor%20to%20detect%20even%20the%20slightest%20movement%20and%20health%20sensors%20for%20pulse%20and%20temperature.%20It%20works%20without%20Wifi%20or%20bluetooth%20and%20has%20a%20range%20of%201-%202%20km%2C%20according%20to%20Hemesh.%20It%20can%20also%20be%20connected%20to%20an%20app%20for%20children%20staying%20far%20away%20to%20monitor%20their%20parents%20movements.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20prototype%20was%20ready%2C%20the%20innovator%20started%20working%20with%20the%20Alzheimer%E2%80%99s%20%26amp%3B%20Related%20Disorders%20Society%20of%20India%20(ARDSI)%20to%20test%2C%20modify%20the%20product%20and%20gain%20insights.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201050px)%20100vw%2C%201050px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2Foriginal_7ef650f7-2