%20to%20see%20the%20small%20impact%20I%E2%80%99ve%20managed%20to%20create%20in%20the%20lives%20of%20these%20families%2C%E2%80%9D%20smiles%20the%20youngster.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Class%2012%20student%20hopes%20to%20get%20the%20product%20up%20and%20running%20in%20the%20next%20six%20months%2C%20after%20his%20Board%20exams.%20He%20plans%20to%20pursue%20a%20degree%20in%20robotics%20while%20continuing%20research%20on%20dementia%20care.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20started%20with%20a%20goal%20of%20creating%20impact%20and%20solving%20problems%20for%20the%20people%20around%20me.%20Now%2C%20I%20want%20to%20create%20solutions%20for%20Alzheimer%E2%80%99s%20and%20take%20India%20to%20the%20forefront%20of%20dementia%20care%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20the%20Alpha%20Monitor%2C%20he%20has%20also%20created%20Universis%2C%20an%20AI%20college%20counsellor%20and%20essay%20review%20app%2C%20CreatoWise%2C%20which%20helps%20you%20grow%20your%20Youtube%20channel%2C%20and%20SessionFix%2C%20a%20platform%20for%20hosting%20paid%20seminars%20and%20courses%20online.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHemesh%20is%20a%20classic%20example%20of%20how%20the%20abundant%20information%20available%20on%20the%20internet%20can%20be%20utilised%20for%20creating%20positive%20change%20and%20impact.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20have%20to%20put%20the%20knowledge%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F334375%2Fnancy-tyagi-instagram-fashion-influencer-inspiring-youtuber-uttar-pradesh%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einternet%20%3C%2Fa%3Eto%20good%20use.%20People%20are%20addicted%20to%20short%20form%20content%2C%20TikTok%2C%20reels.%20People%20like%20me%20use%20the%20internet%20to%20learn%20and%20understand%20concepts.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20vast%20ocean%20of%20information%20that%20is%20helpful%20for%20anyone%20like%20me%20who%20is%20passionate%20about%20learning%20and%20creating%20change%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Hemesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20shows%20us%20that%20with%20the%20right%20use%20of%20the%20internet%2C%20one%20can%20use%20the%20vast%20information%20available%20there%20at%20our%20disposal%20to%20change%20the%20world.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1703860220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2FIMG_4975-min-1703854722-scaled.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D337126%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Looking%20for%20monitors%20for%20elderly%20with%20dementia%3F%20Hemesh%20Chadalavada%20from%20Hyderabad%20has%20created%20Alpha%20Monitor%2C%20a%20wearable%20device%20that%20helps%20caregivers%20monitor%20patients%20with%20dementia%20and%20Alzheimer's.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A14%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F337126%2Fmonitors-for-elderly-hemesh-chadalavada-invents-device-for-dementia%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Two%20Techies%20Are%20Helping%20Foresters%20Combat%20Wildlife%20Crimes%20With%20Technology%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20growing%20modernisation%20and%20increasing%20population%2C%20the%20line%20between%20civilisation%20and%20the%20wild%20has%20become%20increasingly%20blurry.%20For%20the%20most%20part%2C%20humans%20have%20been%20known%20to%20encroach%20upon%20areas%20designated%20for%20the%20wild.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20human-animal%20conflict%20has%20raised%20issues%20worldwide.%20In%20a%20country%20like%20India%2C%20which%20is%20home%20to%20some%20of%20the%20rarest%20animals%20on%20the%20planet%2C%20encompassing%20over%2024%20percent%20of%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F130976%2Findia-forest-tree-green-cover%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20forest%20area%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20rate%20of%20wildlife%20crime%20is%20alarmingly%20high.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20we%20look%20back%20at%20our%20ancestors%2C%20we%20realise%20that%20perpetrating%20atrocities%20upon%20innocent%20wildlife%20has%20been%20a%20sport%20for%20humans.%20Whether%20hunting%20them%20for%20pleasure%20or%20exploiting%20their%20skin%2C%20teeth%2C%20and%20bones%20for%20our%20benefit%2C%20we%20have%20exploited%20them%20for%20ages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20Government%20implementing%20rules%20and%20laws%20to%20protect%20the%20wild%2C%20cases%20of%20wildlife%20crime%20remain%20staggeringly%20high.%20According%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2F112-tigers-deaths-from-january-to-july-this-year-says-wildlife-trust-of-india-1241859.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20in%202020%20alone%2C%20there%20were%20more%20than%201%2C000%20registered%20cases%20of%20wildlife%20crime.%20A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fbangalore%2Ftamil-nadu-highest-number-wildlife-crimes-southern-states-rti-query-8846758%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20states%20that%20in%202023%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%20reported%20150%20cases%20of%20wildlife%20crime%2C%20while%20Karnataka%20reported%2070%20instances%20of%20wildlife%20crimes%20and%2017%20incidents%20of%20poaching.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20with%20a%20judicial%20system%20in%20place%20for%20such%20crimes%2C%20the%20question%20of%20why%20wildlife%20crimes%20are%20on%20the%20rise%20persists.%20Faced%20with%20similar%20concerns%2C%20two%20tech%20enthusiasts%2C%20Allen%20Shaji%20and%20Sobin%20Mathew%20from%20Kerala%20combined%20their%20technological%20expertise%20and%20passion%20for%20the%20wild%20to%20digitally%20document%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F161753%2Fias-hero-uttar-pradesh-tribes-news%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20wildlife%20crimes%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20India.%20This%20not%20only%20eliminates%20bureaucracy%20and%20paperwork%20but%20also%20expedites%20the%20delivery%20of%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFighting%20wildlife%20crime%20with%20technology%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20and%20raised%20in%20Kerala%2C%20Allen%20and%20Sobin%20were%20college%20buddies%20who%20completed%20their%20graduation%20from%20Amalguri%20College%20of%20Engineering%20in%202016.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLike%20any%20other%20engineering%20graduates%2C%20we%20were%20also%20looking%20for%20job%20opportunities.%20I%20got%20placed%20at%20a%20company%20and%20was%20waiting%20for%20the%20offer%20letter%20to%20arrive%20in%202016%20when%20I%20realised%20that%20I%20might%20not%20want%20to%20do%20a%20job%2C%E2%80%9D%20Allen%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2Fagapi-1703858962.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sobin%20Mathew%20and%20Allen%20Shaji%2C%20co-founders%20of%20Leopard%20Tech%20Labs.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2Fagapi-1703858962.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2Fagapi-1703858962-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2Fagapi-1703858962-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2Fagapi-1703858962-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2Fagapi-1703858962-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-337181%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESobin%20Mathew%20and%20Allen%20Shaji%2C%20co-founders%20of%20Leopard%20Tech%20Labs.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Leopard%20Tech%20Labs%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20this%20time%2C%20he%20met%20with%20some%20conservationists%20who%20nudged%20him%20into%20wildlife%20conservation.%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20most%20techies%20are%20into%20finding%20jobs%20and%20getting%20packages%2C%20I%20realised%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332168%2Ftadoba-maharashtra-vacation-sustainable-homestay-by-wildlife-conservation-experts%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewildlife%20conservation%3C%2Fa%3E%20sector%20is%20something%20that%20no%20one%20really%20talks%20about%2C%E2%80%99%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20that%20time%2C%20the%20techies%20weren%E2%80%99t%20delving%20into%20conservation%2C%20and%20technology%20was%20quite%20limited%20in%20this%20field.%20When%20we%20had%20the%20opportunity%20to%20converse%20with%20conservationists%2C%20they%20mentioned%20the%20lack%20of%20certain%20software%20tools.%20Everything%20relied%20heavily%20on%20paperwork%2C%20prompting%20us%20to%20contemplate%20introducing%20innovation%20to%20the%20conservation%20field.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20realised%20how%20there%20is%20a%20gap%20in%20the%20market.%20There%20is%20almost%20zero%20technology%20to%20track%20any%20kind%20of%20wildlife%20crime%20in%20India.%20So%20I%20decided%20to%20join%20hands%20with%20my%20friend%20Sobin%20who%20has%20similar%20interests%20to%20bridge%20this%20gap.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20just%20in%20time%2C%20when%20the%20duo%20was%20looking%20to%20enter%20the%20field%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20looking%20for%20opportunities%20in%20the%20sector%20and%20tried%20reaching%20various%20conservationists.%20We%20met%20with%20Mr%20Jose%20Louie%2C%20who%20also%20was%20from%20our%20hometown.%20He%20was%20from%20the%20Wildlife%20Trust%20Of%20India%20who%20helped%20us%20secure%20our%20first%20project%20with%20them.%20The%20project%2C%20named%20Mapper%2C%20marked%20the%20beginning%20of%20our%20collaboration.%20Upon%20successfully%20completing%20this%20project%2C%20we%20realised%20that%20our%20ideas%20have%20more%20potential%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202017%2C%20they%20incorporated%20the%20company%20%E2%80%98Leopard%20Tech%20Labs%E2%80%99.%20Currently%2C%20they%20have%20launched%20several%20products%20that%20help%20combat%20wildlife%20crime%20and%20have%20a%20customer%20base%20in%20eight%20countries.%20They%20inform%20that%20they%20are%20also%20in%20collaboration%20with%20different%20State%20Governments%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98HAWK%E2%80%99%20for%20speedy%20justice%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20incorporating%20their%20company%2C%20Allen%20and%20Sobin%20began%20working%20as%20consultant%20software%20developers%20for%20the%20Wildlife%20Trust%20of%20India.%20It%20was%20during%20this%20period%20that%20they%20seized%20an%20opportunity%20to%20collaborate%20with%20the%20Kerala%20Forest%20Department.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWorking%20with%20the%20Wildlife%20Trust%20of%20India%20and%20with%20their%20support%2C%20our%20company%20was%20able%20to%20make%20HAWK%20or%20Hostile%20Activity%20Watch%20Kernel%20with%20the%20forest%20department%20of%20Kerala%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2Fagapi-1-1703859196.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22representative%20image%20only%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2Fagapi-1-1703859196.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2Fagapi-1-1703859196-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2Fagapi-1-1703859196-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2Fagapi-1-1703859196-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2Fagapi-1-1703859196-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-337182%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIn%202023%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%20reported%20150%20cases%20of%20wildlife%20crime%2C%20while%20Karnataka%20reported%2070%20instances%20of%20wildlife%20crimes%20and%2017%20incidents%20of%20poaching.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kerala%20forest%20department%20or%20most%20forest%20departments%20in%20the%20country%20relied%20heavily%20on%20manual%20records%20of%20crimes%20and%20cases.%20The%20Kerala%20forest%20department%20has%20now%20switched%20to%20a%20digital%20documenting%20process%20in%20a%20first-of-its-kind%20initiative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHAWK%20is%20an%20offence%20management%20system%20that%20includes%20case%20handling%2C%20court%20case%20monitoring%2C%20communication%20management%2C%20and%20wildlife%20death%20monitoring.%20This%20module%20encompasses%20various%20functions%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CBefore%20its%20implementation%2C%20all%20processes%20were%20managed%20through%20paperwork.%20With%20the%20software%20in%20place%2C%20users%20simply%20input%20the%20data%2C%20and%20the%20system%20automatically%20generates%20reports%20in%20formats%20such%20as%20PDF%2C%20ready%20for%20submission%20to%20the%20court.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20has%20built%20an%20analytics%20module%20along%20with%20a%20communication%20module.%20For%20instance%2C%20if%20a%20question%20arises%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F166751%2Fhero-parliament-attack-terrorists-crpf-delhi-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ein%20the%20Parliament%20%3C%2Fa%3Eabout%20the%20number%20of%20wildlife%20deaths%20in%20Kerala%20from%20January%201%20to%20February.%20The%20system%20provides%20the%20required%20data%20with%20a%20single%20click%20and%20within%20seconds%2C%20enabling%20efficient%20analysis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20how%20the%20software%20works%2C%20Allen%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CUsers%20can%20quickly%20retrieve%20data%20on%20specific%20wildlife%20incidents%2C%20like%20the%20number%20of%20elephant%20deaths%20from%20electrocution%20or%20tigers%20lost%20to%20hunting.%20The%20system%20provides%20data%20in%20formats%20such%20as%20Excel%2C%20PDF%2C%20graphs%2C%20and%20Google%20Maps%2C%20offering%20insights%20into%20the%20geographical%20distribution%20of%20incidents.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20it%20allows%20higher%20authorities%20to%20monitor%20the%20status%20of%20cases%2C%20whether%20pending%20at%20the%20range%20or%20division%20level%20or%20submitted%20to%20the%20court.%20This%20functionality%20streamlines%20review%20meetings%2C%20facilitates%20prompt%20actions%20based%20on%20case%20progress%2C%20and%20provides%20speedy%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20this%20data%2C%20the%20company%20collaborates%20with%20various%20NGOs%20and%20Government%20agencies.%20Currently%2C%20they%20are%20in%20collaboration%20with%20NGOs%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20IUCN%2C%20IFaw%2C%20WTI%2C%20Kerala%20Forest%20Department%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Forest%20Department%2C%20Mudumalai%20Tiger%20Reserve%2C%20Periyar%20Tiger%20Reserve%2C%20Parambikulam%20Tiger%20Reserve%2C%20and%20Species%20Survival%20Commission%20(SSC).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20HAWK%2C%20the%20company%20has%20several%20other%20products%20such%20as%20SARPA%20%E2%80%94%20Snake%20Awareness%2C%20Rescue%20and%20Protection%20App%2C%20Jumbo%20Radar%20%E2%80%94%20a%20comprehensive%20tool%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noref