e%20aeroponic%20towers.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2FMacrogardens-2-1703855363.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2FMacrogardens-2-1703855363-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2FMacrogardens-2-1703855363-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2FMacrogardens-2-1703855363-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2FMacrogardens-2-1703855363-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-337146%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EPrakhar%20and%20Tanay%20launched%20%E2%80%98Macrogardens%E2%80%99%20to%20make%20aeroponic%20towers.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Prakhar%20explains%20how%20the%20aeroponic%20tower%20can%20revolutionise%20farming%20in%20cities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMeant%20for%20balconies%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrakhar%2C%20a%20computer%20science%20graduate%20by%20education%2C%20was%20always%20passionate%20about%20growing%20his%20own%20vegetables.%20Other%20than%20ornamental%20plants%2C%20he%20wanted%20to%20grow%20veggies%20on%20his%20balcony%20but%20without%20opting%20for%20a%20tedious%20soil-based%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20when%20I%20came%20across%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F327478%2Fashwin-sawant-low-cost-hydroponics-model-helps-farmers-grow-fodder-save-water%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esoilless%20hydroponic%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20aeroponic%20systems.%20While%20hydroponics%20requires%20a%20horizontal%20system%20using%20PVC%20pipes%20that%20end%20up%20taking%20up%20a%20lot%20of%20space%2C%20I%20want